  "prompt": "What does \"followed by None\" mean in Instagram search?",
  "response": "When you see \"followed by None\" in an Instagram search, it means that the account you are looking at is not being followed by any of the Instagram users that you are currently following. This feature helps you understand the connection between the account you're searching for and the people you follow on Instagram.",
